in the RAIO App every single day.

255
00:12:16.050 --> 00:12:17.900
That's a nonnegotiable.

256
00:12:17.930 --> 00:12:19.100
Every single day.

257
00:12:19.130 --> 00:12:23.340
And then I recommend taking one to two
conversation or private classes weekly

258
00:12:23.360 --> 00:12:25.500
to put into practice what
you're learning here.

259
00:12:25.530 --> 00:12:27.640
Build confidence speaking and get rid

260
00:12:27.670 --> 00:12:30.700
of that fear and shame and mental block.

261
00:12:30.720 --> 00:12:32.340
Remember, you can download the audio

262
00:12:32.370 --> 00:12:34.980
and the transcript if you
want down here below.

263
00:12:35.000 --> 00:12:36.907
If you want to practice outside
of course.

264
00:12:37.107 --> 00:12:37.860
Don't take any notes.

265
00:12:37.880 --> 00:12:39.980
Let the RAIO App do
the work for you, right?

266
00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:42.580
All right, remember,
you can go to the next section,

267
00:12:42.600 --> 00:12:45.460
when you're able to answer all
the questions in the interactive version

268
00:12:45.490 --> 00:12:49.540
correctly, out loud, on time,
without looking at the transcript, okay?

269
00:12:49.570 --> 00:12:51.980
And remember, input creates output.

270
00:12:52.010 --> 00:12:53.060
Input creates output.

271
00:12:53.080 --> 00:12:54.420
So be patient, okay?

272
00:12:54.450 --> 00:12:57.340
It is very, very,
very normal that you will understand all

273
00:12:57.370 --> 00:13:00.260
these things, but you can't
say them for a long time.

274
00:13:00.290 --> 00:13:02.660
And that is just how
language learning works.

275
00:13:02.690 --> 00:13:06.380
We just need to keep exposing ourselves
to the English language,

276
00:13:06.410 --> 00:13:11.500
expand our vocabulary, and we will
slowly start to speak automatically.

277
00:13:11.530 --> 00:13:12.540
Okay?

278
00:13:12.570 --> 00:13:15.260
Repeat after me before you continue.

279
00:13:15.290 --> 00:13:17.260
I'll become fluent in English.

280
00:13:17.290 --> 00:13:21.920
I'll never give up on my goal.

281
00:13:27.880 --> 00:13:29.380
Awesome.
Perfect.

